<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>APEAPCET 2024</title>
    <style>
        * {
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        #home {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        #nav {
            height: 60px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: rgb(124, 124, 228);
        }
        #nav #eamcet {
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        #nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 0 10px;
           
        }
        
        #nav a:hover {
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); 
        }
        
        #intro {
            padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        #intro h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        #intro p {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .do {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: rgb(124, 124, 228);
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .do:hover {
            background-color: rgb(94, 94, 208);
        }
        #About {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background-color: lightgrey;
            text-align: center;
        }
        #About h2 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        #About p {
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        #trending {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .card h3 {
            color: rgb(124, 124, 228);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .card p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
        }
        #details {
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        form {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .gapping {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .gapping label {
            display:block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .gapping input[type="text"],
        .gapping input[type="tel"],
        .gapping input[type="email"],
        .gapping input[type="number"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .gapping input[type="radio"] {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .required {
            color: red;
        }
        input[type="submit"] {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: rgb(124, 124, 228);
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        input[type="submit"]:hover {
            background-color: rgb(94, 94, 208);
        }
        footer {
            display:flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height:50px;
            background-color: #333;
            color:white;
        }
        .trend
        {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 30px;
        }
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            #nav {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                height: auto; 
            }
        
            #nav #eamcet {
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                padding-left:10px ;
            }
        
            #nav a {
                margin: 5px 0;
                padding: 10px 0; 
                color: white; 
                padding-left: 10px;
            }
            
        
            #trending {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(1, 1fr);
            }
        
            #details form {
                max-width: 100%;
            }
        }
        
        @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            #intro h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
        
            #intro p {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
        
            .card {
                padding: 15px;
            }
        
            .card h3 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
        
            .card p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="home">
        <div id="nav">
            <h2 id="eamcet">APEAPCET 2024</h2>
            <a href="#home" >Home</a>
            <a href="/top" >Top Colleges</a>
            <a href="https://cets.apsche.ap.gov.in/EAPCET/PDF/APEAPCET2024_Notification_V2.pdf" >Notifications</a>
            <a href="https://cets.apsche.ap.gov.in/EAPCET/EapcetHomepages/ImportantDates.aspx" >Important Dates</a>
        </div>
        <div id="intro">
            <h1>Welcome to APEAPCET 2024</h1>
            <p>Your gateway to top engineering and pharmacy colleges in Andhra Pradesh.</p>
            <a href="#form" class="do">Find Your College</a>
        </div>
        <div id="About">
            <h2>About EAPCET</h2>
            <p>The Andhra Pradesh Engineering, Agriculture, and Pharmacy Common Entrance Test (APEAPCET) is a crucial examination for students aspiring to pursue undergraduate courses in engineering, agriculture, and pharmacy in Andhra Pradesh. This exam assesses the knowledge and aptitude of candidates, serving as a gateway to prestigious colleges and universities in the state. Stay informed with the latest updates, notifications, and important dates to ensure a successful application and admission process.</p>
        </div>
